        H(i) = 1-tau*v*v'. Here tau is a scalar which is stored  in  TauQ[i],  and
        vector v has the following  structure:  v(0:i-1)=0, v(i)=1, v(i+1:m-1)  is
        stored   in   elements   A(i+1:m-1,i).   Matrix   P  is  as  follows:  P =
